data.description: This Colonial home in Gurnee is now available and is situated on a large .7 acre corner lot, consisting of four spacious bedrooms with two and one-half baths. The bright kitchen boasts beautiful quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, and hardwood flooring. The dining room, family and living room areas incorporate modern vinyl plank flooring. This home is perfect for any growing families looking for more space inside & out! Newer carpet on the upper level, which comprises all four bedrooms, including the master bedroom and en-suite bath walk-in shower. The basement is partially finished, currently holding a full gym. For any dog lovers out there, the current owners have you covered with a built-in dog run to keep your convenience in mind and yard in-tact. This home also comes with an American Home Shield Home Warranty for added piece of mind. Be sure to schedule your showing today while this home is still available!
